    "updated_at": "2013-04-20T19:02:52Z",
    "body": "The other use case for this is if you're implementing a function on a trait that is marked `unsafe` because an implementation for _some other_ type needs to be unsafe, but _this_ type implementation doesn't need to be.\n",
